

1 Hemu at am i tashogi g Jesus Christ hegai matsh haschu am hab wo e juh pi shaꞌi mehk iꞌajed. Jiosh ash am ahgid matsh am wo t-chehgi ahchim mach d piongaj. Tki heg am hema i kei g anghil. T id am ni-chehgi ahni John mani d piongaj g Jesus Christ. 2 Kuni ia oꞌohan hegai mani haschu i neid. Ihda ni-oꞌohana o d Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch d hegai wohokam mat am i maskogi g Jesus. 3 Jiosh at wo wa s-ha hoꞌigeꞌel hegam mat am wo i neꞌokchul ch hegam mat ab wo kaihamad. E ash aihim mat am hab wo e juh wehs ihda gam hu baꞌich haꞌichu ahga mant in wo oꞌoha. 

**Oꞌohana am ha wui g wewaꞌak dakam Jesus Ihmdam **

4-5 Am ant wo i em-oꞌohani ahpim wewaꞌak dakam Jesus Christ ihmdam am Asia chekshani ch ed. 

Ab at wo wa baꞌich i s-em-hoꞌigeꞌidad ch ab baꞌich wo i em-mahkad g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam g t-ohg Jiosh ch Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag ch Jesus Christ. T-ohg Jiosh o chum hekid an haꞌichug. K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag am wehmaj ch wewaꞌak masma e chehgidch am t-wehhejed. K g Jesus Christ si s-ap am i t-tashogid g wohokam ch d hegai mat si wehpeg ab uhpam s-ap i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed k am hahawa ha dahm g wehs kokownal id dahm jewed. 

Ab o si t-tatchua ch heg hekaj e muhkid t-wehhejed k t-doꞌibia ab pi ap t-chuꞌijig amjed 6 k hab t-juh mach d hahawa piongaj g t-ohg Jiosh ch am wo i ahgahid g haꞌichu ahgaj. Jesus Christ o wehs uꞌukch g gewkdag. Kutt ab wo ihmad chum hekid. 

7 Neh, e o aihim mat ep wo jiwia ab dahm kahchim amjed. Wehs hemajkam at wo neidad, chum wa hegam mat ab sisish kots t ab. Wehs nahnko mahs hemajkam at wo shoshani heg hekaj. 

8 T-kownalig Jiosh o wehs uꞌukch g gewkdag ch hab kaij, “Ahni ani d alpha ch d omega.” Idam o d si wehpeg ch si oidchkam oꞌohana. K hab ahg g Jiosh mo si wehpeg an haꞌichug ch si ha oidch an wabsh wo kia haꞌichugk. 

**Matsh g jesus am i e Maskogi John wui **

9 Dani em-wehm wohochuddam ahni John nach pi ab t-hemakochudch g Jesus Christ wehm. Ni am em-wehm apꞌedag Jiosh kownaltalig ed ch hekaj em-wehm ni-shoꞌigchud. An amt ni-wua heg ab al sikod jewed mo hab chehgig Patmos ch am haꞌichug shuhdagi ch ed nani wa pi si s-gewkam ahgahim g Jiosh neꞌoki ch hegai wohokam mat g Jesus am i tashogi. 

10 K am hu hebai d domig tash. Ni ab ihm g Jiosh. K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag am si i ni-wehmaj. Kuni kah mat ab hema si s-kaidam neo ab ni-wehgaj k hab sha kaidag mat g kuikud ab ku 11 k hab kaij, “An g oꞌohan mapt haschu wo i nei k am haha wo ha cheha mat am wo i bei ihda oꞌohana hegam ha wui wewaꞌak dakam Jesus ihmdam amai Ephesus t am ch Smyrna t am ch Pergamum t am ch Thyatira t am ch Sardis t am ch Philadelphia t am ch amai Laodicea t am.” 

12 Neh, nt ab si sikol i kekiwua mant wo nei mas hedai ab ni-wui neok k haha wabsh nei mo g wewaꞌak ohla lalampa an dadha chuhchakud t an. 13 K am ha shahgid hema kehk ch hab mahs mo g Jiosh si Kehsha. K g lihwaj ged hu si ais g tahtdaj. K g ohla giwud an hab juhkch e bahsho. 14 K g moꞌoj si s-tohta hab masma mo g s-wihs gew. K g wuhpuij si s-masma tonod hab masma mo g s-toni nahda. 15 K g tahtdaj si s-wegima tonod hab masma mo g kohwli hahgig. K g neꞌokij hab masma hab kaidag mo g si geꞌe shuhdagi an med. 16 Id o an uꞌukch g wewaꞌak huhuꞌu s-apko e-nowi ed ch an kamshch g is-pahyo. K id ab i wuhshanis chinij ab. K g wuhioshaj shaꞌi si tonod hab masma mo g tash tonlig dahm juhk. 

17 Kunt am i neidok ab i gei wecho hab sha masma mo g muhki. 

Kut an ni-tahtam k hab kaij, “Pi g am shaꞌi ni-ehbenid. Dani ahni mani si wehpeg ia haꞌichug ch chum hekid ia wo haꞌichugk. 18 Am ant wa chum ni-muhkid k uhpam ep ni-chegito k chum hekid d haha wo doakamk. Am ani dahm gewkdag g muhkig ch am dahm gewkdag amai mo am haꞌichug g koꞌi. 

19 “Pegih, am g oꞌohan map haschu i neid mat hab wo e juh hemu ch haschu hab wo e juh imhab i dahm. 20 Am ant wo m-ahgi g s-aꞌagi haꞌichu ab amjed idam wewaꞌak huhuꞌu mani in uꞌukch ch idam wewaꞌak lalampa. Idam wewaꞌak lalampa o d hegam ni-ihmdam mo am kihdag hegam ha eda wewaꞌak kihhim. K idam wewaꞌak huhuꞌu o d ha-wanimeddam.” 

